caption: okay this is insane — 200 million YouTube, 100 million Spotify, and still in the Global charts — WHO ARE YOU PEOPLE?! 😍🙌🏾👑🔥 #pasoori #love #gratitude

one year ago, when @zulfiqarjkhan heard this tune I’d sent him on a voicenote, he told me with tremendous calm that it will enter the global charts. i laughed, drank my coffee, and put it out of mind. today, i woke up to this… insanely happy for @abdullah.s.siddiqui @shaegilll @sherrykhattak and @zulfiqarjkhan — many many congratulations to us, and a EDDA VADDA thanks to all you lovers — dildaars and sab yaars — who are pow-ing this #pasoori at the GLOBAL LEVEL 😭🌈🙏🏾🕺🏿💃🏾🤳🏾❤️❤️❤️
#pasoori (and me!) in @newyorkermag ❤️‍🔥❤️‍🔥❤️‍🔥 loved talking to @primattoo about the song’s meaning and construction (and my first trip to fire island..) 🤲🏾 link in biooo, pasoori paaiyooo 💃🏾💃🏾💃🏾

maha-thanks to director @kamalkay and art director @hashimali90 for converting my wild (WhatsApp-flooding) ideas into this earthy, dusky, somehow very truthful video about the way we live and love 💌💌💌 Also: those classical dance moves from @sheemakermani changed my life 🥺🌈🙏🏾

COACHELLVA BALAMVA 🌸🌸🌸 thank u @iamfahadhussayn for sending this mughal angarkha in the mail, thank u @therajakumari & @leokalyan for singing with me onstage, and thank u @coachella for the cute pics 🙏🏾 there is no representation without inclusion, and i was so thrilled to see our manifold, many-splendored family light up the gobi tent ❤️❤️❤️ also thanking pooja in the last slide, twaada jazba bemisaal ay 🙌🏾🙌🏾
